<!-- EDIT1 SECTION "FAQ:" [1-20] -->
<h2 class="sectionedit2"><a name="how_do_i_use_the_ninja_rope_with_a_single_key_like_lierox" id="how_do_i_use_the_ninja_rope_with_a_single_key_like_lierox">How do I use the ninja rope with a single key like LieroX?</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
There is a way to use a single key for the ninja rope in Gusanos by using some console command trickery.
</p>

<p>
Add this to your <a href="doku.php?id=main:general_docs:faq:usage:general:config" class="wikilink1" title="main:general_docs:faq:usage:general:config">config.cfg</a> file or <a href="doku.php?id=main:general_docs:faq:usage:general:console" class="wikilink1" title="main:general_docs:faq:usage:general:console">open the console</a> and enter:
</p>
<pre class="code">bind &lt;key&gt; &quot;+P0_CHANGE;+P0_JUMP;-P0_CHANGE&quot; (eg. bind p &quot;+P0_CHANGE;+P0_JUMP;-P0_CHANGE&quot;)</pre>

</div>
<!-- EDIT2 SECTION "How do I use the ninja rope with a single key like LieroX?" [21-] --></div>
